- Basic land (Mountain) found and put on battlefield tapped ✓
- Library shuffled (17→16 cards) ✓

### Test 3: Validation
```bash
make validate
```
**Result**: All 406 tests pass ✓

## Related Issues

- mtg-fe5398: Priority after special actions (FIXED)
- mtg-e00cb8: Tracking epic for missing player choices"
